  + [status] is verified_wsl
  + [effort] is S-M
  + [risk] is medium
  + [depends_on] is SLM-19, SLM-26, SLM-28
  + [scope] is normalize provider, lexicon, support, contradiction, and lineage refs for stable primer re-ingestion
